    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like shine with zero stone chips, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear or creasing. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and stored in a climate-controlled environment. It truly represents the pinnacle of its model, offering a like-new driving experience for the most discerning buyer.",
