    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every aspect of this automobile\u2014from the mirror-finish paintwork to the pristine, smoke-free interior\u2014reflects a life of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically indistinguishable from a showroom model, this unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in its absolute peak state. We invite serious inquiries for a private viewing of this investment-grade automobile.",
