    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it\u2019s finally ready for its next adventure. You won't find a single blemish or hiccup here; it\u2019s a total dream to drive. Come take a look and fall in love!",
