      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its factory-intended performance envelope. The S54B32 straight-six features a dual-VANOS system recently serviced with upgraded seals, and the rod bearings have been addressed for long-term reliability. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its original kinematics via refreshed bushings. Finished in original paint with no signs of oxidative stress, this specimen boasts a factory-correct interior with zero bolster fatigue. A mechanically superlative example for the purist collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
