    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines showroom quality. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, and has been protected with a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to an interior that remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and the cabin still carries that distinctive new-car aroma. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented from day one and zero leaks or mechanical noises. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new machine. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who refuses to settle for anything less than perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
